{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1090,"text":"Wow, this is bright."},{"time":3121,"text":"It must use a lot of power."},{"time":6112,"text":"Well, flying you all in here"},{"time":7604,"text":"must have cost a bit of energy too."},{"time":10052,"text":"So the whole planet needs a lot of energy,"},{"time":12970,"text":"and so far we've been running mostly on fossil fuel."},{"time":15871,"text":"We've been burning gas."},{"time":17920,"text":"It's been a good run."},{"time":19307,"text":"It got us to where we are, but we have to stop."},{"time":22175,"text":"We can't do that anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24329,"text":"So we are trying different types of energy now,"},{"time":26610,"text":"alternative energy,"},{"time":27824,"text":"but it proved quite difficult to find something"},{"time":30322,"text":"that's as convenient and as cost-effective"},{"time":33123,"text":"as oil, gas and coal."},{"time":35940,"text":"My personal favorite is nuclear energy."},{"time":40030,"text":"Now, it's very energy-dense,"},{"time":42631,"text":"it produces solid, reliable power,"},{"time":45112,"text":"and it doesn't make any CO2."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47495,"text":"Now we know of two ways"},{"time":48987,"text":"of making nuclear energy: fission and fusion."},{"time":54161,"text":"Now in fission, you take a big nucleus,"},{"time":56506,"text":"you break it in part, in two,"},{"time":58141,"text":"and it makes lots of energy,"},{"time":59688,"text":"and this is how the nuclear reactor today works."},{"time":61901,"text":"It works pretty good."},{"time":63310,"text":"And then there's fusion."},{"time":65464,"text":"Now, I like fusion. Fusion's much better."},{"time":67870,"text":"So you take two small nuclei,"},{"time":69564,"text":"you put it together, and you make helium,"},{"time":72070,"text":"and that's very nice."},{"time":73428,"text":"It makes lots of energy."},{"time":74974,"text":"This is nature's way of producing energy."},{"time":77574,"text":"The sun and all the stars in the universe"},{"time":79982,"text":"run on fusion."},{"time":82227,"text":"Now, a fusion plant"},{"time":84123,"text":"would actually be quite cost-effective"},{"time":86438,"text":"and it also would be quite safe."},{"time":88428,"text":"It only produces short term radioactive waste,"},{"time":92861,"text":"and it cannot melt down."},{"time":94893,"text":"Now, the fuel from fusion comes from the ocean."},{"time":97420,"text":"In the ocean, you can extract the fuel"},{"time":99238,"text":"for about one thousandth of a cent"},{"time":101128,"text":"per kilowatt-hour, so that's very, very cheap."},{"time":103459,"text":"And if the whole planet would run on fusion,"},{"time":106847,"text":"we could extract the fuel from the ocean."},{"time":108291,"text":"It would run for billions and billions of years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111555,"text":"Now, if fusion is so great, why don't we have it?"},{"time":115327,"text":"Where is it?"},{"time":116663,"text":"Well, there's always a bit of a catch."},{"time":118511,"text":"Fusion is really, really hard to do."},{"time":121749,"text":"So the problem is, those two nuclei,"},{"time":124233,"text":"they are both positively charged,"},{"time":125861,"text":"so they don't want to fuse."},{"time":127652,"text":"They go like this. They go like that."},{"time":129429,"text":"So in order to make them fuse,"},{"time":130393,"text":"you have to throw them at\neach other with great speed,"},{"time":132580,"text":"and if they have enough speed,"},{"time":133493,"text":"they will go against the repulsion,"},{"time":135327,"text":"they will touch, and they will make energy."},{"time":137480,"text":"Now, the particle speed"},{"time":139887,"text":"is a measure of the temperature."},{"time":141657,"text":"So the temperature required for fusion"},{"time":143399,"text":"is 150 billion degrees C."},{"time":146561,"text":"This is rather warm,"},{"time":148392,"text":"and this is why fusion is so hard to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151838,"text":"Now, I caught my little fusion bug"},{"time":153863,"text":"when I did my Ph.D. here at the\nUniversity of British Columbia,"},{"time":157533,"text":"and then I got a big job in a laser printer place"},{"time":160585,"text":"making printing for the printing industry."},{"time":163123,"text":"I worked there for 10 years,"},{"time":165375,"text":"and I got a little bit bored,"},{"time":167055,"text":"and then I was 40, and I got a mid-life crisis,"},{"time":170008,"text":"you know, the usual thing:"},{"time":171641,"text":"Who am I? What should I do?"},{"time":174100,"text":"What should I do? What can I do?"},{"time":176686,"text":"And then I was looking at my good work,"},{"time":178738,"text":"and what I was doing is I was cutting the forests"},{"time":180789,"text":"around here in B.C."},{"time":182144,"text":"and burying you, all of you,"},{"time":183738,"text":"in millions of tons of junk mail."},{"time":187180,"text":"Now, that was not very satisfactory."},{"time":189115,"text":"So some people buy a Porsche."},{"time":191380,"text":"Others get a mistress."},{"time":194151,"text":"But I've decided to get my bit"},{"time":195825,"text":"to solve global warming and make fusion happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200088,"text":"Now, so the first thing I did"},{"time":201819,"text":"is I looked into the literature and I see,"},{"time":204248,"text":"how does fusion work?"},{"time":206990,"text":"So the physicists have been\nworking on fusion for a while,"},{"time":210132,"text":"and one of the ways they do it"},{"time":211448,"text":"is with something called a tokamak."},{"time":213754,"text":"It's a big ring of magnetic coil,"},{"time":216484,"text":"superconducting coil,"},{"time":217810,"text":"and it makes a magnetic field"},{"time":219160,"text":"in a ring like this,"},{"time":220948,"text":"and the hot gas in the middle,"},{"time":222340,"text":"which is called a plasma, is trapped."},{"time":224470,"text":"The particles go round and round and round"},{"time":226218,"text":"the circle at the wall."},{"time":227658,"text":"Then they throw a huge amount of heat in there"},{"time":229186,"text":"to try to cook that to fusion temperature."},{"time":231660,"text":"So this is the inside of one of those donuts,"},{"time":233988,"text":"and on the right side you can see"},{"time":235320,"text":"the fusion plasma in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237460,"text":"Now, a second way of doing this"},{"time":239708,"text":"is by using laser fusion."},{"time":242108,"text":"Now in laser fusion, you have a little ping pong ball,"},{"time":244228,"text":"you put the fusion fuel in the center,"},{"time":246274,"text":"and you zap that with a whole\nbunch of laser around it."},{"time":249204,"text":"The lasers are very strong, and it squashes"},{"time":250908,"text":"the ping pong ball really, really quick."},{"time":252634,"text":"And if you squeeze something hard enough,"},{"time":254589,"text":"it gets hotter,"},{"time":255964,"text":"and if it gets really, really fast,"},{"time":257360,"text":"and they do that in one billionth of a second,"},{"time":259678,"text":"it makes enough energy and enough heat"},{"time":261581,"text":"to make fusion."},{"time":262917,"text":"So this is the inside of one such machine."},{"time":264994,"text":"You see the laser beam and the pellet"},{"time":266837,"text":"in the center."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268386,"text":"Now, most people think that fusion is going nowhere."},{"time":271348,"text":"They always think that the physicists are in their lab"},{"time":274280,"text":"and they're working hard, but nothing is happening."},{"time":276095,"text":"That's actually not quite true."},{"time":277615,"text":"This is a curve of the gain in fusion"},{"time":279607,"text":"over the last 30 years or so,"},{"time":281799,"text":"and you can see that we're making now"},{"time":283357,"text":"about 10,000 times more fusion than we used to"},{"time":286190,"text":"when we started."},{"time":287264,"text":"That's a pretty good gain."},{"time":288259,"text":"As a matter of fact, it's as fast"},{"time":290245,"text":"as the fabled Moore's Law"},{"time":291945,"text":"that defined the amount of transistors"},{"time":294149,"text":"they can put on a chip."},{"time":295666,"text":"Now, this dot here is called JET,"},{"time":298671,"text":"the Joint European Torus."},{"time":300094,"text":"It's a big tokamak donut in Europe,"},{"time":302524,"text":"and this machine in 1997"},{"time":305594,"text":"produced 16 megawatts of fusion power"},{"time":308818,"text":"with 17 megawatts of heat."},{"time":310976,"text":"Now, you say, that's not much use,"},{"time":312781,"text":"but it's actually pretty close,"},{"time":314492,"text":"considering we can get"},{"time":315532,"text":"about 10,000 times more than we started."},{"time":317839,"text":"The second dot here is the NIF."},{"time":320452,"text":"It's the National Ignition Facility."},{"time":322738,"text":"It's a big laser machine in the U.S.,"},{"time":325264,"text":"and last month they announced"},{"time":326541,"text":"with quite a bit of noise"},{"time":328394,"text":"that they had managed to make more fusion energy"},{"time":330552,"text":"from the fusion"},{"time":332142,"text":"than the energy that they put in \nthe center of the ping pong ball."},{"time":334998,"text":"Now, that's not quite good enough,"},{"time":336823,"text":"because the laser to put that energy in"},{"time":338523,"text":"was more energy than that,"},{"time":340255,"text":"but it was pretty good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342295,"text":"Now this is ITER,"},{"time":344022,"text":"pronounced in French: EE-tairh."},{"time":346080,"text":"So this is a big collaboration of different countries"},{"time":349211,"text":"that are building a huge magnetic donut"},{"time":351066,"text":"in the south of France,"},{"time":353010,"text":"and this machine, when it's finished,"},{"time":355018,"text":"will produce 500 megawatts of fusion power"},{"time":357796,"text":"with only 50 megawatts to make it."},{"time":360196,"text":"So this one is the real one."},{"time":361382,"text":"It's going to work."},{"time":362114,"text":"That's the kind of machine that makes energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364306,"text":"Now if you look at the graph, you will notice"},{"time":366062,"text":"that those two dots are a little bit"},{"time":367567,"text":"on the right of the curve."},{"time":368609,"text":"We kind of have fallen off the progress."},{"time":370545,"text":"Actually, the science to make those machines"},{"time":372534,"text":"was really in time"},{"time":374070,"text":"to produce fusion during that curve."},{"time":376906,"text":"However, there has been a bit of politics going on,"},{"time":379645,"text":"and the will to do it was not there,"},{"time":381777,"text":"so it drifted to the right."},{"time":383455,"text":"ITER, for example, could have been built"},{"time":385511,"text":"in 2000 or 2005,"},{"time":387362,"text":"but because it's a big international collaboration,"},{"time":389807,"text":"the politics got in and it delayed it a bit."},{"time":392255,"text":"For example, it took them about three years"},{"time":393879,"text":"to decide where to put it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395447,"text":"Now, fusion is often criticized"},{"time":397983,"text":"for being a little too expensive."},{"time":399583,"text":"Yes, it did cost"},{"time":401124,"text":"a billion dollars or two billion dollars a year"},{"time":403160,"text":"to make this progress."},{"time":404353,"text":"But you have to compare that to the cost"},{"time":405943,"text":"of making Moore's Law."},{"time":407183,"text":"That cost way more than that."},{"time":409071,"text":"The result of Moore's Law"},{"time":410589,"text":"is this cell phone here in my pocket."},{"time":412525,"text":"This cell phone, and the Internet behind it,"},{"time":414754,"text":"cost about one trillion dollars,"},{"time":417434,"text":"just so I can take a selfie"},{"time":420665,"text":"and put it on Facebook."},{"time":423239,"text":"Then when my dad sees that,"},{"time":424740,"text":"he'll be very proud."},{"time":427920,"text":"We also spend about 650 billion dollars a year"},{"time":431828,"text":"in subsidies for oil and gas"},{"time":434130,"text":"and renewable energy."},{"time":435760,"text":"Now, we spend one half of a percent of that on fusion."},{"time":439934,"text":"So me, personally, I don't think it's too expensive."},{"time":442582,"text":"I think it's actually been shortchanged,"},{"time":444362,"text":"considering it can solve all our energy problems"},{"time":446754,"text":"cleanly for the next couple of billions of years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449428,"text":"Now I can say that, but I'm a little bit biased,"},{"time":452088,"text":"because I started a fusion company"},{"time":453976,"text":"and I don't even have a Facebook account."},{"time":456534,"text":"So when I started this fusion company in 2002,"},{"time":461917,"text":"I knew I couldn't fight with the big lads."},{"time":464759,"text":"They had much more resources than me."},{"time":466336,"text":"So I decided I would need to find a solution"},{"time":468576,"text":"that is cheaper and faster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470463,"text":"Now magnetic and laser fusion"},{"time":472373,"text":"are pretty good machines."},{"time":473804,"text":"They are awesome pieces of technology,"},{"time":475245,"text":"wonderful machines, and they have shown"},{"time":477119,"text":"that fusion can be done."},{"time":478598,"text":"However, as a power plant,"},{"time":480552,"text":"I don't think they're very good."},{"time":482423,"text":"They're way too big, way too complicated,"},{"time":484480,"text":"way too expensive,"},{"time":485618,"text":"and also, they don't deal very much"},{"time":487374,"text":"with the fusion energy."},{"time":488648,"text":"When you make fusion, the energy comes out"},{"time":490406,"text":"as neutrons, fast neutrons comes out of the plasma."},{"time":493074,"text":"Those neutrons hit the wall of the machine."},{"time":495334,"text":"It damages it."},{"time":496719,"text":"And also, you have to catch\nthe heat from those neutrons"},{"time":498683,"text":"and run some steam to spin a turbine somewhere,"},{"time":501116,"text":"and on those machines,"},{"time":502400,"text":"it was all a bit of an afterthought."},{"time":505031,"text":"So I decided that surely there\nis a better way of doing that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508182,"text":"So back to the literature,"},{"time":509466,"text":"and I read about the fusion everywhere."},{"time":511458,"text":"One way in particular attracted my attention,"},{"time":514180,"text":"and it's called magnetized target fusion,"},{"time":516270,"text":"or MTF for short."},{"time":518858,"text":"Now, in MTF, what you want to do"},{"time":521300,"text":"is you take a big vat"},{"time":523270,"text":"and you fill that with liquid metal,"},{"time":525286,"text":"and you spin the liquid metal"},{"time":526806,"text":"to open a vortex in the center,"},{"time":528454,"text":"a bit like your sink."},{"time":529590,"text":"When you pull the plug on a sink, it makes a vortex."},{"time":531694,"text":"And then you have some pistons driven by pressure"},{"time":534090,"text":"that goes on the outside,"},{"time":535566,"text":"and this compresses the liquid metal"},{"time":537486,"text":"around the plasma, and it compresses it,"},{"time":539248,"text":"it gets hotter, like a laser,"},{"time":540902,"text":"and then it makes fusion."},{"time":542128,"text":"So it's a bit of a mix"},{"time":543048,"text":"between a magnetized fusion"},{"time":544703,"text":"and the laser fusion."},{"time":546686,"text":"So those have a couple of very good advantages."},{"time":549459,"text":"The liquid metal absorbs all the neutrons"},{"time":551802,"text":"and no neutrons hit the wall,"},{"time":553558,"text":"and therefore there's no damage to the machine."},{"time":555694,"text":"The liquid metal gets hot,"},{"time":557150,"text":"so you can pump that in a heat exchanger,"},{"time":559150,"text":"make some steam, spin a turbine."},{"time":561030,"text":"So that's a very convenient way of doing"},{"time":562209,"text":"this part of the process."},{"time":563469,"text":"And finally, all the energy to make the fusion happen"},{"time":567060,"text":"comes from steam-powered pistons,"},{"time":569195,"text":"which is way cheaper than lasers"},{"time":570851,"text":"or superconducting coils."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572745,"text":"Now, this was all very good"},{"time":574233,"text":"except for the problem that it didn't quite work."},{"time":576737,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":578607,"text":"There's always a catch."},{"time":579903,"text":"So when you compress that,"},{"time":581417,"text":"the plasma cools down"},{"time":583341,"text":"faster than the compression speed,"},{"time":584969,"text":"so you're trying to compress it,"},{"time":586282,"text":"but the plasma cooled down and\ncooled down and cooled down"},{"time":588617,"text":"and then it did absolutely nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590558,"text":"So when I saw that, I said,\nwell, this is such a shame,"},{"time":592593,"text":"because it's a very, very good idea."},{"time":594343,"text":"So hopefully I can improve on that."},{"time":596697,"text":"So I thought about it for a minute,"},{"time":597792,"text":"and I said, okay, how can we make that work better?"},{"time":599869,"text":"So then I thought about impact."},{"time":601727,"text":"What about if we use a big hammer"},{"time":603561,"text":"and we swing it and we hit the nail like this,"},{"time":606093,"text":"in the place of putting the hammer on the nail"},{"time":608067,"text":"and pushing and try to put it in? That won't work."},{"time":610262,"text":"So what the idea is"},{"time":612193,"text":"is to use the idea of an impact."},{"time":613937,"text":"So we accelerate the pistons with steam,"},{"time":616019,"text":"that takes a little bit of time,"},{"time":617298,"text":"but then, bang! you hit the piston,"},{"time":619281,"text":"and, baff!, all the energy is done instantly,"},{"time":621833,"text":"down instantly to the liquid,"},{"time":623429,"text":"and that compresses the plasma much faster."},{"time":625479,"text":"So I decided, okay, this is good, let's make that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627927,"text":"So we built this machine in this garage here."},{"time":631652,"text":"We made a small machine"},{"time":632737,"text":"that we managed to squeeze"},{"time":634709,"text":"a little bit of neutrons out of that,"},{"time":636357,"text":"and those are my marketing neutrons,"},{"time":638558,"text":"and with those marketing neutrons,"},{"time":640001,"text":"then I raised about 50 million dollars,"},{"time":642600,"text":"and I hired 65 people. That's my team here."},{"time":645490,"text":"And this is what we want to build."},{"time":647072,"text":"So it's going to be a big machine,"},{"time":648586,"text":"about three meters in diameter,"},{"time":650060,"text":"liquid lead spinning around,"},{"time":651862,"text":"big vortex in the center,"},{"time":653454,"text":"put the plasma on the top and on the bottom,"},{"time":655774,"text":"piston hits on the side,"},{"time":657200,"text":"bang!, it compresses it,"},{"time":658710,"text":"and it will make some energy,"},{"time":659994,"text":"and the neutron will come out in the liquid metal,"},{"time":662386,"text":"going to go in a steam engine and make the turbine,"},{"time":664986,"text":"and some of the steam will go back"},{"time":666492,"text":"to fire the piston."},{"time":667490,"text":"We're going to run that about one time per second,"},{"time":669380,"text":"and it will produce 100 megawatts of electricity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674764,"text":"Okay, we also built this injector,"},{"time":676449,"text":"so this injector makes the plasma to start with."},{"time":678736,"text":"It makes the plasma at about"},{"time":680451,"text":"a lukewarm temperature of three million degrees C."},{"time":684426,"text":"Unfortunately, it doesn't last quite long enough,"},{"time":686633,"text":"so we need to extend the life\nof the plasma a little bit,"},{"time":689768,"text":"but last month it got a lot better,"},{"time":691400,"text":"so I think we have the plasma compressing now."},{"time":693985,"text":"Then we built a small sphere, about this big,"},{"time":696541,"text":"14 pistons around it,"},{"time":698007,"text":"and this will compress the liquid."},{"time":700331,"text":"However, plasma is difficult to compress."},{"time":702436,"text":"When you compress it,"},{"time":703225,"text":"it tends to go a little bit crooked like that,"},{"time":705777,"text":"so you need the timing of the piston"},{"time":707385,"text":"to be very good,"},{"time":708481,"text":"and for that we use several control systems,"},{"time":711153,"text":"which was not possible in 1970,"},{"time":713355,"text":"but we now can do that"},{"time":714747,"text":"with nice, new electronics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718039,"text":"So finally, most people think that fusion"},{"time":720568,"text":"is in the future and will never happen,"},{"time":722720,"text":"but as a matter of fact, fusion is getting very close."},{"time":725814,"text":"We are almost there."},{"time":726890,"text":"The big labs have shown that fusion is doable,"},{"time":729527,"text":"and now there are small companies\nthat are thinking about that,"},{"time":731834,"text":"and they say, it's not that it cannot be done,"},{"time":734195,"text":"but it's how to make it cost-effectively."},{"time":736300,"text":"General Fusion is one of those small companies,"},{"time":738453,"text":"and hopefully, very soon, somebody, someone,"},{"time":741771,"text":"will crack that nut,"},{"time":743054,"text":"and perhaps it will be General Fusion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":744628,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746407,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}